AWS IAM services allow to create user, group user, policites, and type of accesses granded to those users under the group. 
Region matter, some services are not allow at specific regions. 
Assign permission to AWS services. IAM ROle, used for EC2 instances. 
Create role for EC2 instance. Go to the Role -> create role -> choose EC2 => fill out all requirements => choose the access allow under the drop down menu.
REMEMBER: DO NOT USE ROOT(~) ACCOUNT at least it's for creating account. 
create budget for AWS services and manage the budget.
CI/CD: continuous interation, continous delivery

